Utility class:
- specialty type of class that contains only static methods(can call class through its name)
   and no instance variable
    -> main purpose: provide a set of useful and commonly used functions
                     that can be easily accessed and reused
    ->make code more readable and maintainable
    ->have built-in utility classes such as Arrays Math etc
    -> can create custom utility class
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Arrays utility class methods

- toString(arrVar): returns string representation of content of Arrays
- equals(arrVar1, arrVar2):returns boolean, checks if Arrays are equal or not
- sort (arrVar): sorts the elements of Arrays in ascending order
- binarySearch (arrVar): searches for specific element in Array with help of binary search algor.
                        Array must be sorted in ascending order
- copyOf(arrVar, length): copies specific Array and returns new array
- copyOfRange(arrVar, from, to): returns new Array, copies specific range of specified Array
- fill(arrVar, value): assigns specified value to each element of specified Array.
- deepToString(arrVar): returns a string representation of multi-dimensional array
- asList(arrVar): returns fixed-size list backed by specified arrays
